            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>In Christi nomine. Breve pro futuris temporibus a memoria abenda vel
                        retinenda in presentia <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/218"
                            >Ildibrandi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> et <persName>Rolandi</persName> filii bone
                        memorie <persName>Teuderichi</persName> et <persName>Tarberti qui Corbulino
                            vocatur</persName> filii bone memorie <persName>Petri</persName> et
                            <persName>Tegrini</persName> filii <persName>Anselmi</persName>,
                            <persName>Roine</persName> filii bone memorie et
                            <persName>Rolandi</persName> filii bone memorie
                            <persName>Ildibrandi</persName> et <persName>Arduini</persName> et
                            <persName>Signorello</persName> filii bone memorie
                            <persName>Mili</persName> et <persName>Alberti</persName> filii bone
                        memorie [...] et <persName>Sapurello</persName> filio
                            <persName>Segnurelli</persName> et <persName>Rodulfo</persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/367">Caldanelle</placeName> et <persName>Bonini
                            qui [...] vocatur</persName> et <persName>Widi</persName> filii
                            <persName>Rodulfi</persName> et reliquis plures. Ibique in eorum
                        presentia veniens <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/210"
                            >Andreas</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> cum <persName key="#Advocatus">Petro</persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus">avocato</rs> suo filio bone memorie
                            <persName>Racteri</persName> cum Sancta Dei evangelia in manibus suis
                        sic iurare voluit de ipsa <rs key="#Monasteries">abatia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti
                            Bartolomei</orgName> Apostoli que est infra <rs key="#Comitatus"
                            >comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/154">Roselle</geogName> et est
                        constructa in loco qui dicitur <placeName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#places/281">Sestinghe</placeName> prope <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvi</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers">Brama</placeName> in presentia <persName
                            key="#Missus_regis">Althomo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Missus_regis">misso donni imperatoris</rs> quod de predicto
                        monasterio consuetudo non fui neque <rs key="#Fodrum">fodero</rs> neque
                            <rs>parrata</rs> ab imperatore neque a suo misso non dedisse neque dedi
                        qui iam dicto monasterio fuit edificato a tempore <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/130">Henrici</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs>. Cum prefato Altohomo missu donni
                        imperatoris taliter vidisse et audisse quod prefato Petro avocato de prefato
                        monasterio in presentia de prefatis hominibus paratus abveni cum Sancta Dei
                        evangelia quod iurare volebat hoc supra legitur, tunc prenominato misso
                        propter Deum et anime donni <persName key="#Emperor/king">Corradi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs> et <persName>Ghisle</persName>
                        uxore sua et <persName ref="#people/237">Henrici</persName> filii eius et
                            <persName>Cuniunda</persName> nurua sua ipsum sacramentum perdunavit qui
                        non ei rectum comparuisset propterea pius non fui. Hoc factum est in anno
                        Domini nostri Iesu Christi anni ab incarnatione eius millesimo tricesimo
                        octavo, regnante donno nostro Conrado gratia Dei imperatore augustus anni
                        imperii eius Deo propitio in Italia undecimo, VIII idus martii, indictione
                        sexta. Factum est in loco qui dicitur <placeName ref="#places/366"
                            >Corduliano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Comitatus">territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/154">Rosellense</geogName>.
                            <persName key="#Judge">Walfredus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> sacri palatii ibi fuit. <persName key="#Judge"
                            >Gherardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> donni imperatoris ibi fuit. <persName
                            key="#Notary">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> ibi fuit et hunc breve scripsi.</ab>
